snippets.title: contentwarehouse CreateDocumentSchema Sample
snippets.description: CreateDocumentSchema creates a document schema.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse DeleteDocumentSchema Sample
snippets.description:
DeleteDocumentSchema deletes a document schema. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document schema does
not exist. Returns BAD_REQUEST if the document schema has documents
depending on it.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse GetDocumentSchema Sample
snippets.description:
GetDocumentSchema gets a document schema. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document schema does not
exist.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse GetOperation Sample
snippets.description: GetOperation is a utility method from google.longrunning.Operations.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse ListDocumentSchemas Sample
snippets.description: ListDocumentSchemas lists document schemas.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse UpdateDocumentSchema Sample
snippets.description:
UpdateDocumentSchema updates a Document Schema. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if the name of the
Document Schema is non-empty and does not equal the existing name.
Supports only appending new properties, adding new ENUM possible values,
and updating the
[EnumTypeOptions.validation_check_disabled][google.cloud.contentwarehouse.v1.EnumTypeOptions.validation_check_disabled]
flag for ENUM possible values. Updating existing properties will result
into INVALID_ARGUMENT.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse CreateDocument Sample
snippets.description: CreateDocument creates a document.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse DeleteDocument Sample
snippets.description: DeleteDocument deletes a document. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document does not exist.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse FetchAcl Sample
snippets.description:
FetchAcl gets the access control policy for a resource. Returns NOT_FOUND error if
the resource does not exist. Returns an empty policy if the resource exists
but does not have a policy set.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse GetDocument Sample
snippets.description: GetDocument gets a document. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document does not exist.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse GetOperation Sample
snippets.description: GetOperation is a utility method from google.longrunning.Operations.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse LockDocument Sample
snippets.description: LockDocument lock the document so the document cannot be updated by other users.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse SearchDocuments Sample
snippets.description:
SearchDocuments searches for documents using provided
[SearchDocumentsRequest][google.cloud.contentwarehouse.v1.SearchDocumentsRequest].
This call only returns documents that the caller has permission to search
against.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse SetAcl Sample
snippets.description:
SetAcl sets the access control policy for a resource. Replaces any existing
policy.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse UpdateDocument Sample
snippets.description:
UpdateDocument updates a document. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if the name of the document
is non-empty and does not equal the existing name.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse GetOperation Sample
snippets.description: GetOperation is a utility method from google.longrunning.Operations.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse RunPipeline Sample
snippets.description: RunPipeline run a predefined pipeline.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse CreateRuleSet Sample
snippets.description: CreateRuleSet creates a ruleset.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse DeleteRuleSet Sample
snippets.description: DeleteRuleSet deletes a ruleset. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document does not exist.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse GetOperation Sample
snippets.description: GetOperation is a utility method from google.longrunning.Operations.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse GetRuleSet Sample
snippets.description: GetRuleSet gets a ruleset. Returns NOT_FOUND if the ruleset does not exist.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse ListRuleSets Sample
snippets.description: ListRuleSets lists rulesets.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse UpdateRuleSet Sample
snippets.description:
UpdateRuleSet updates a ruleset. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if the name of the ruleset
is non-empty and does not equal the existing name.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse CreateSynonymSet Sample
snippets.description:
CreateSynonymSet creates a SynonymSet for a single context.
Throws an ALREADY_EXISTS exception if a synonymset already exists
for the context.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse DeleteSynonymSet Sample
snippets.description:
DeleteSynonymSet deletes a SynonymSet for a given context.
Throws a NOT_FOUND exception if the SynonymSet is not found.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse GetOperation Sample
snippets.description: GetOperation is a utility method from google.longrunning.Operations.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse GetSynonymSet Sample
snippets.description:
GetSynonymSet gets a SynonymSet for a particular context.
Throws a NOT_FOUND exception if the Synonymset
does not exist

snippets.title: contentwarehouse ListSynonymSets Sample
snippets.description: ListSynonymSets returns all SynonymSets (for all contexts) for the specified location.

snippets.title: contentwarehouse UpdateSynonymSet Sample
snippets.description:
UpdateSynonymSet remove the existing SynonymSet for the context and replaces it
with a new one.
Throws a NOT_FOUND exception if the SynonymSet is not found.
